-- S. Africa Low Interest Rate Not Enough to Spur Growth: Marcus
-- B y   N i k i   M o o r e
-- 2012-06-07T18:32:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/s-africa-low-interest-rate-not-enough-to-spur-growth-marcus.html
South Africa’s low interest rates
aren’t enough to stimulate the economy alone, Reserve Bank
Governor Gill Marcus said in a speech in Durban today.  The Bank is mindful of the effect that inflation targeting
has on  job creation , she said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
